tweet: Happy Birthday Cardano. Like all authors, I'll always remember that whatever I create is only made great by those inspired by it. Thank you for an amazing year. The next one will be even greater.  https://t.co/kf6nkIUoX0

One year ago, Cardano successfully launched its mainnet. Since then, our project has progressed and with it, our global community has grown! Check out our infographic on the Cardano community. And we thank you for your continued support! #CardanoMainnetAnniversary  https://t.co/SK5UayGwIl

In January of this year, we held our first meetup in London, UK! It was a huge success with people coming from far and wide! Since then, our meetup groups have all grown immensely with 39 groups across 27 countries. #CardanoMainnetAnniversary  https://t.co/ltuIn29KEA

We held our first official Webcast on January 15th with IOHK’s Charles Hoskinson and Duncan Coutts and Cardano Foundation’s Michael Parsons and Jon Moss! You can still watch it here:  https://t.co/VOvJHknO3U  #CardanoMainnetAnniversary  https://t.co/o9xslpB8lA

By December 20th, Distributed Futures, sponsored by Cardano Foundation, held its first official event together presenting their research paper on: Smart Ledger Geostamping - Steps Towards Interoperability & Standards #CardanoMainnetAnniversary  https://t.co/ZL8zm9tJQe
#Kraken new listings...   Keep an eye on #Cardano (#ADA) And #Quantam (#QTUM)..  https://t.co/JFdYvuEMGt
